eBoard is a sw/hw project to make an electronic score board,
which will be used on Martial Arts championship.

- 2 points markers     / one per player
- 2 faults indicators  / one per player
- buttons for add points (1,2,3 points)  / one per player
- button for add faults / one per player

The display will have two colour, one for each player: blue/red.
